Exercise 3: Calculation of the electron energy loss spectrum (EELS) of bulk silicon
            using the turbo_eels.x program.

 Step 1. Run the SCF ground-state calculation

    mpirun -np 2 /scratch/itimrov/temp_13_QE_school_v.5.2.0/espresso-5.2.0/bin/pw.x < Si.scf.in |tee Si.scf.out

 Step 2. Perform Lanczos recursions using turbo_eels.x 

    mpirun -np 2 /scratch/itimrov/temp_13_QE_school_v.5.2.0/espresso-5.2.0/bin/turbo_eels.x < Si.eels.in |tee Si.eels.out

 Step 3. Run the spectrum calculation

    mpirun -np 2 /scratch/itimrov/temp_13_QE_school_v.5.2.0/espresso-5.2.0/bin/turbo_spectrum.x < Si.tddfpt_pp.in |tee Si.tddfpt_pp.out

 Step 4. Plot the spectrum using "gnuplot" and the script "plot_spectrum.gnu". 

    gnuplot -> load 'plot_dispersion.gnu'

    evince Spectrum.eps

